dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Illustrations include two cherubs and a barrell of wine and grapes framing the scale cartouche, ships on the ocean, and the French coat of arms in the upper right corner of the map. Does not match any states listed in Van der Krogt. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 35 x 49 cm.
